| `ExternalKnowledgeGraphGateway` | `core/interfaces/knowledge_graph.py` | External KG lookup (Wikidata, DBpedia, ConceptNet) |
| `RetrieverGateway` | `core/interfaces/retriever.py` | High-level retrieval abstraction |
| `ConversationMemoryGateway` | `core/interfaces/conversation_memory.py` | Conversation history |
