| `AgentRegistryGateway` | `core/interfaces/agent_registry.py` | HMAS agent discovery + routing |
| `AgentOrchestratorGateway` | `core/interfaces/agent_orchestrator.py` | Multi-agent plan/execute |
| `WorkflowEngineGateway` | `core/interfaces/workflow_engine.py` | Stateful agent graph execution (LangGraph) |
| `ToolGateway` | `core/interfaces/tool.py` | Agent-callable tool abstraction |
| `ChainGateway` | `core/interfaces/chain.py` | LLM chain composition (batch + streaming) |
