| `RerankerGateway` | `core/interfaces/reranker.py` | Search result reranking |
| `PromptTemplateGateway` | `core/interfaces/prompt_template.py` | Structured prompt management (Jinja2) |
| `GuardrailGateway` | `core/interfaces/guardrail.py` | Input/output safety validation |
| `ObservabilityGateway` | `core/interfaces/observability.py` | AI tracing and telemetry |

### AI Data Flow

```
Document → Loader → Splitter → Embedder → VectorStore
                                              ↓
Query → Embedder → VectorStore.search → Reranker → LLM.complete → Guardrail → Response
                   KnowledgeGraph.query ↗

Goal → Orchestrator → [Agent₁, Agent₂, …] → Tool calls → Review → Answer

Goal → WorkflowEngine (LangGraph StateGraph)
         ├─ Router → Planner → Executor → Reviewer → Router (loop)
         ├─ Checkpointing (PostgreSQL prod / SQLite staging / memory dev)
         └─ Final Answer

Evaluation: LLM Output → Evaluator (LLM-as-judge) → EvalResult (score, passed, reason)

MCP Server ← FastMCP + streamable-http + structured output (outputSchema)
  ├─ Tools: search_documents, complete_text, run_rag_query, query_knowledge_graph, evaluate_output, ...
  ├─ Resources: config://ai-settings, status://health
  └─ Prompts: rag_query, summarize_document, extract_entities
```
